Class Passenger

java.lang.Object
com.inFlight.shared.model.Passenger
public class Passenger extends Object
Passenger is a class that represents a passenger in the application. It contains information about the passenger ID, username, password, nova credits, and checkout status. POJO (Plain Old Java Object) class.

      public Passenger(int passengerId, String username, String password, int novaCredits, boolean checkedOut)
      Constructor to create a Passenger object with specified passenger ID, username, password, nova credits, and checkout status.
      Parameters:
      passengerId - the ID of the passenger
      username - the username of the passenger
      password - the password of the passenger
      novaCredits - the nova credits (in Application currency) of the passenger
      checkedOut - the checkout status of the passenger

    • Passenger

      public Passenger(String username, String password, int novaCredits)
      Constructor to create a Passenger object with specified username, password, and nova credits. The passenger ID is set to -1 and the checkout status is set to false by default.
      Parameters:
      username - the username of the passenger
      password - the password of the passenger
      novaCredits - the nova credits (in Application currency) of the passenger
